                  <p>
                    This is a <b>front-end REACT.js</b> based web project.
                    Stat-Tracker is a website that can track your video game
                    stats using an API provided by "tracker.gg". You need to
                    provide your <b>username and platform</b> and the website
                    will search for the query and provide you with all the stats
                    available.
                    <br />
                    <br />
                    This website can be used by the millions of gamers who play
                    these games to track their stats and see what they can do to
                    be better. They can figure out the places they are strong in
                    and the places they are weak and train accordingly to
