                  </p>
                  <h1>Features</h1>
                  <p>
                    Stat-Tracker is a fully <b>responsive website</b> and it
                    scales well with mobile view as well. This website is made
                    with <b>scalability</b> in mind. It is easily scalable with
                    new data inputted in the already existing games and new
                    games added within the <b>API</b>. This website uses
                    <b>REACT Hooks</b> including
                    <b>useState, useEffect, global context, etc.</b>, along with
                    <b>React-DOM & CORS.</b> It also uses
                    <b>Bootstrap</b> components.
                  </p>
